for Japan , 2011 be dominate by the earthquake and tsunami in March .
the disaster lead to unprecedented number of japanese help one another .
after the tsunami smash into Japan 's north - east coast on 11 March , kill thousand and engulf entire community , people 's stoicism and they determination to pull together win international praise .
in April the then prime minister Naoto Kan thank the world for its help in a letter entitle " Kizuna - the bond of friendship " .
and when Japan unexpectedly beat the United States to win the woman 's football World Cup , " kizuna " forge by the player ' teamwork be cite with pride .
half a million people take part in the annual poll for the kanji character , conduct by Japan 's Kanji Aptitude Testing Foundation .
about 60,000 people nominate " kizuna " , but the runner - up be much less optimistic : " wazawai " mean disaster .
for some japanese , 2011 bring the opposite of " kizuna " .
a firm that specialise in divorce ceremony say in July that they have triple since the tsunami as people reassess they life .
